# TAILWIND SYSTEM RULES (FacePe)

## Source of truth

- Canonical values: `docs/design-system.md`, layout: `docs/component-library.md`, responsive: `docs/responsive-system.md`.
- Figma reference: file `Jms4ZsFFmzbAI1LyBO0x1E` (Home `3139:29850`, Verify `3139:31023`).
- **Extend** `tailwind.config.js` (`theme.extend`) with FacePe tokens—**do not** paste raw Figma hex in HTML except during one-off spikes (then immediately promote to config).

## General

- **Utility philosophy:** compose with **semantic utilities** (`text-ink-900`, `bg-surface-page`) mapped in config; fall back to closest Tailwind default only when token not yet defined.
- **Responsive:** mobile-first; see `docs/responsive-system.md` for breakpoint intent.
- **Components:** repeated patterns → `@layer components` **or** small HTML partials with documented class strings (avoid 40-line chains duplicated 4×).

## Spacing

- **Section padding:** `py-10 md:py-[60px]`; horizontal `px-4 sm:px-8 lg:px-[100px]`.
- **Allowed scale:** Tailwind spacing scale **`4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 16, 20, 24, 32`**; for Figma-exact **`60`**, **`100`**, use **`theme.extend.spacing`** (`60: '60px'`, `gutter: '100px'`) so markup stays `px-gutter` not arbitrary brackets.
- **Grid gaps:** `gap-8` (product grid), `gap-5` (CTA pairs), `gap-4` (hero title stack).

## Typography

- **Headings:** map Figma sizes to extended `fontSize` keys: `display-home` (`64px/1.3`), `display-verify` (`68px/1.3`), `heading-2` (`44px/50px`).
- **Tracking:** `tracking-tight` + extended `letterSpacing.tight-hero: '-0.14875rem'` (~`-2.38px` @ 16 root) for hero only.
- **Weights:** `font-medium` (nav), `font-bold` (CTAs, headings).

## Colors

- Register extended palette from `docs/design-system.md` (`ink-*`, `brand-600`, `lilac-*`, `border-*`, `surface-*`).
- **Gradients:** single `bg-gradient-primary` utility via `backgroundImage` in config (`to 98%` stop for parity with Figma).
- **Borders:** default `border-border-subtle` on outline buttons + nav.

## Radius

- `rounded-pill` → `9999px` on `h-14` buttons **or** explicit `58px` via extended `borderRadius.pill`.
- `rounded-card` → `28px`.
- `rounded-tile` → `16px`.

## Shadows

- Define `boxShadow.card`, `boxShadow.chip`, `boxShadow.primary` per design-system doc—reference by name in HTML.

## Custom CSS

- **Allowed:** `@layer base` for font-face; `@layer components` for `.faq-row`, `.segmented-steps`; CSS variables if preferred over long Tailwind config.
- **Avoid:** per-page `style=""`, `!important` chains, magic numbers not in tokens.

## Class ordering (suggested)

`layout → box → spacing → typography → color → border → shadow → state → motion → responsive`

## DO NOT

- Introduce extra accent colors or second brand gradients.
- Animate `width`, `height`, `margin`, `top` (layout thrash).
- Use `mix-blend-mode` on text for “effect” unless explicitly designed.
